Sistema May Expand $100 Million Buyback on Price, RIA Reports

-- B y   T o r r e y   C l a r k
-- 
2011-10-05T10:00:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-05/sistema-may-expand-100-million-buyback-on-price-ria-reports.html
AFK Sistema may expand a $100 million
buyback program for its own shares and depositary receipts and
stock of its OAO Mobile TeleSystems unit if prices remain low,
RIA Novosti reported, citing Chief Executive Officer Mikhail
Shamolin.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Torrey Clark at 
 tclark8@bloomberg.net  